Package org.hibernate.internal.log

Interface UnsupportedLogger

  • @MessageLogger(projectCode="HHH")
@ValidIdRange(min=90002001,
              max=90003000)
public interface UnsupportedLogger
    Class to consolidate logging about usage of features which should never be used. Such features might have been introduced for practical reasons so that people who really know what they want can use them, with the understanding that they should find a better alternative.
